page.title: 11A NORMAL SCHOOOL DAY
page.content: I get up at 8.oo,o clock.Have a wash and clean my teeth.Then I have my breakfast and then put my school uniform on.When I am ready I get my bags ready.Then we go to school we walk. Mr Cartwright our teacher teachs us Maths, English, Sience, Art and Phisical Education.We go out to play at 10.30 am then dinner is at 12.oo noon until 1300.We leave school at 3.10 pm I walk home. I watch t.v .Then we go uptown to Hillards.Then we go home.Then we have our tea.My dad comes home 6.10 pm .Then my dad takes me to my Aunties.Then we come home my dad goes back to work.Then I watch t.v.Then I go and feed my three fish.Then I go and have a wash.Then I go to bed .Sometimes I watch my t.v.or I read before I go to sleep.
